<HL>
   Newmont Deal
   With American
   Barrick Fails
   ---
   Gold Mining Firms Call Off
   $2.8 Billion Merger, Keep
   Joint Venture Talk Alive
   ----
   By Larry M. Greenberg and Marj Charlier
   Staff Reporters of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
07/19/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A2
</SO>
